	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S. D.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Pacis capita ita, ut accepi a d. <persName ref="p8033" cert="high">Beza</persName> et <persName ref="p540" cert="high">Calvino</persName>, mitto ea lege, ut remittas.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Scribit Aurelia 29. martii <persName ref="p8033" cert="high">Beza</persName> meliorem potuisse componi, si nonnulli auxilio domini fuissent usi, et quidem articulos hos recipi ab aliis, repudiari ab aliis.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l492" cert="high">Argentorato</placeName> scribitur pacis capita esse recepta ideoque socrum <placeName type="auto_name">Condensis</placeName> una cum liberis per nobiles equites e Gallia missos reduci iterum in Galliam cum gaudio; interim vero, cum <placeName ref="l378" cert="high">Parisienses</placeName> se opponant paci et fere papistae in aliis locis, exercitum nondum esse dimissum, sed compositis rebus mox dimittendum.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Dominus adsit suis!</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ex <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l830" cert="high">Anglia</placeName> scribitur omnia esse in tuto et felicia, deo gratia.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Celebrant nunc <persName type="auto_name">Londini</persName> comitia regni; capite plexi sunt 7, qui insidiati sunt vitae reginae; gravia edicta instituuntur contra rebelles reginae in Anglia; vae episcopis et praelatis!</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">In <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2524" cert="high">Scotia</placeName> omnia bene habent, nisi quod Guysiaca regina adhuc invitis principibus missat et quidem sola.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Venit huc ante duos menses aulicus <persName type="auto_name">Prutenorum</persName> principis concionator, <persName type="auto_name">Georgius Weigelius</persName>, vir pius et doctissimus, principi charissimus; is contraxit nobiscum amicitiam etc.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Contulit iussu principis cum <persName ref="p458" cert="high">Brentio</persName> etc.; longa est historia; ocium scribendi non suppetit.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Mittam quaedam eius scripta, sed ut tuto remittas.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Da sähend ir, wohar das liegen kumpt wider den churfürsten amm <placeName type="citizen_name">Rhyn</placeName>, da sähend ir, wie wir mitt der warheit articulieren möchtind wider dise unruͤwige, uffruͤrige nequam.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto">An vero respondendum sit hisce calumniosis articulis et retundenda mendatia in illorum colla et ora, cogitabo.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><foreign xml:lang="de">O hette ich me muͦß, wyl und krefften</foreign> et non ita oppressus essem, ne vix hiscere possem etc.!</s>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Sed dabit dominus consilium.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Mitto item catechesin principis et illam dono sorori tuae, matronae optimae.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Libellum modo de fractione panis remitte; si allata fuerint exempla <placeName ref="l157" cert="high">Franckforto</placeName>, curabo, ut habeatis.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="18" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Wie were imm, wenn die rüstung imm tütschen land gienge uff <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l306" cert="high">Meyland</placeName>, dem rych under <persName type="auto_name">Maximilianen</persName> wider zuͦ bringen, und darzuͦ die Wälschen hulffind?</s>
					<s n="19" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Mussitatur hac de re nescio quid.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="20" xml:lang="de" type="auto"><foreign xml:lang="la">Ego certi nihil hac de re affirmo;</foreign> ich sich aber wol, das ein verdeckt ässen kochet wirt.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="21" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Dominus adsit nobis et servet ab omni malo!</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="22" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Sororem, fratrem, nepotes, omnes amicos saluta; mei omnes vos salvere iubent.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="23" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vale.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="24" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tiguri, die Georgii 1563.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="25" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tuus ex animo ille.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="26" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Clarissimo viro d. <persName ref="p8055" cert="high">Ambrosio Blaurero</persName> <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l287" cert="high">Lütmerchae</placeName> in <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l774" cert="high">Durgavia</placeName> agenti, domino meo honorando et fratri longe charissimo.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
